          <h2 class="section-heading mb-4">
            <span class="section-heading-upper">Caelum</span>
            <span class="section-heading-lower">visual web crawler</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-3">Hyperlinks facilitate the navigation from one web resource to another. Links are an integral part of how users experience the web as they provide a path through the vast quantity of online resources. 
          </p>
          <p class="mb-3">The Caelum Web Crawler is a tool to allow a curious user to explore the links emanating from their favorite web page. Sign up for our FREE NO STRINGS ATTCHED service you will be able to provide a URL of interest and see the path of links in an interactive visualization!   
          </p>
          <p class="mb-3">We provide the option to crawl the web in a breadth first or depth first manor. The breadth first option will explore ALL the links from each level of the node of interest before moving down to the next level. The depth first search will explore links in a given chain down as many levels as possible before exploring a new chain. 
          </p>
          <p class="mb-3">The visualizations provide a unique and informative view of real world websites for users to explore the differences between depth first and breadth first traversals.  So sign up for an account or start a new search! 
          </p>
